<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Smart Crop Advisory</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">🌱 SmartCrop</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#advisory">Advisory</a>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn">☰</button>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="tag">AI-BASED FARMING SUPPORT</p>
        <h1>Smart Crop Advisory for Small and Marginal Farmers</h1>
        <p>
          Get crop recommendations, fertilizer suggestions, weather-based alerts,
          and practical farming guidance for better yield.
        </p>
        <a href="#advisory" class="primary-btn">Get Crop Advice</a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="weather-icon">☀️</div>
        <h3>Today's Farm Update</h3>
        <p><strong>Temperature:</strong> 31°C</p>
        <p><strong>Humidity:</strong> 68%</p>
        <p><strong>Rain Chance:</strong> 25%</p>
        <span class="status">Good day for irrigation planning</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="advisory-section" id="advisory">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="tag">PERSONALIZED RECOMMENDATION</p>
        <h2>Get Your Crop Advisory</h2>
        <p>Enter your farm details to receive a basic crop recommendation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="advisory-container">
        <form id="advisoryForm" class="advisory-form">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="soil">Soil Type</label>
            <select id="soil" required>
              <option value="">Select soil type</option>
              <option value="black">Black Soil</option>
              <option value="red">Red Soil</option>
              <option value="clay">Clay Soil</option>
              <option value="sandy">Sandy Soil</option>
              <option value="loamy">Loamy Soil</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="season">Season</label>
            <select id="season" required>
              <option value="">Select season</option>
              <option value="kharif">Kharif</option>
              <option value="rabi">Rabi</option>
              <option value="summer">Summer</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="water">Water Availability</label>
            <select id="water" required>
              <option value="">Select availability</option>
              <option value="low">Low</option>
              <option value="medium">Medium</option>
              <option value="high">High</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="land">Land Area (Acres)</label>
            <input type="number" id="land" min="0.1" step="0.1" placeholder="Example: 1.5" required />
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="primary-btn full-btn">Generate Advisory</button>
        </form>

        <div class="result-card" id="resultCard">
          <div class="result-placeholder">
            <div class="result-icon">🌾</div>
            <h3>Your advisory will appear here</h3>
            <p>Fill in the farm details and click “Generate Advisory”.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features" id="features">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="tag">FARMER SUPPORT</p>
        <h2>How SmartCrop Helps Farmers</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>Crop Recommendation</h3>
          <p>Suggests suitable crops based on soil, season, land area, and water availability.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌦️</div>
          <h3>Weather Alerts</h3>
          <p>Provides weather-related guidance for irrigation, sowing, and harvesting decisions.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">🧪</div>
          <h3>Fertilizer Guidance</h3>
          <p>Gives simple fertilizer recommendations to support healthy crop growth.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
          <h3>Better Yield Planning</h3>
          <p>Helps farmers plan resources efficiently and reduce avoidable crop losses.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tips-section">
      <div>
        <p class="tag">FARMING TIP</p>
        <h2>Check soil moisture before irrigation</h2>
        <p>Over-irrigation can damage roots and waste water. Water crops based on soil moisture and crop stage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tip-icon">💧</div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer id="contact">
    <div>
      <h3>🌱 SmartCrop Advisory</h3>
      <p>Supporting small and marginal farmers with smarter agricultural decisions.</p>
    </div>
    <p>© 2026 Smart Crop Advisory System</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
